1.-->// MAKING COMMENT OF SELECTED LINES           : Select the lines then "ctrl + /".
2.-->// RENAME THE FILE                            : F2 {In this laptop, F2 key alone will not work. press fn key+F2}.
3.-->// TO KNOW ABOUT A HEADER FILE                : Press ctrl and click on that header file.
4.-->// MAKING MORE THAN ONE CURSOR                : Hold alt key and click on the places where you want to make cursors. Press end key, the cursor will come to end of the line.
